  <figcaption>All figures are read, unaltered, from instrument 016's frozen, sha256-pinned census
  (<code>results.json</code>, sample <code>fb79e81c&hellip;</code>) and verified first-hand this session; every
  Protocol phrase is quoted verbatim from the source PDF (see below). Wilson 95% intervals are shown on
  every rate. Small N is on the face of each row (live arm n=25).</figcaption>
